%0D%0A%0D%0AResults%3A+Risk+factors+of+the+death+because+of+severe+HFMD+children+included+female%2C+aged+1+%7E+3+years%2C+enterovirus%0D%0A71+infection%2C+falling+ill+in+winter%2C+more+than+one+children+in+home%2C+being+taken+care+of+by+grandparents%2C+the%0D%0Acaregivers%E2%80%99+education+not+more+than+9+years%2C+having+fever+more+than+3+days%2C+consciousness+disorders%2C+general%0D%0Aweakness%2C+vomiting%2C+general+weakness%2C+abnormal+pupillary+light+reflex%2C+repeated+cough%2C+tachypnea%2C+moist+rales%2C%0D%0Awhite+frothy+sputum%2C+pink+frothy+sputum%2C+and+cyanosis+on+lips+or+the+whole+body%2C+tachycardia%2C+arrhythmia%2C+cold%0D%0Alimbs%2C+pale+complexion%2C+weakened+pulse.+%28all+p+%3C+0.05%29.+Spatial-temporal+analysis+detected+high-value+clusters%2C+the%0D%0Amost+likely+cluster+located+at+rural+countries+in+the+northern+parts+of+Chongqing%2C+from+January%2C+2015+to+July%2C+2017.%0D%0A%28p+%3C+0.01%29.+Besides%2C+some+urban+districts+were+also+found+high+incidence+of+severe+HFMD+cases+according+to+the%0D%0Aincidence+maps.%0D%0A%0D%0AConclusions%3A+The+detection+of+clinical+risk+factors+and+the+temporal%2C+spatial+and+socio-demographic+distribution%0D%0Aepidemiological+characteristics+of+severe+HFMD+contribute+to+the+timely+diagnosis+and+intervention%2C+the+results+of%0D%0Athis+study+can+be+the+reference+of+further+clinical+and+public+health+practice.%22%3Bs%3A5%3A%22image%22%3Bs%3A21%3A%22epidomonology.PNG.PNG%22%3Bs%3A9%3A%22opac_hide%22%3Bs%3A1%3A%220%22%3Bs%3A8%3A%22promoted%22%3Bs%3A1%3A%221%22%3Bs%3A6%3A%22labels%22%3BN%3Bs%3A9%3A%22frequency%22%3BN%3Bs%3A16%3A%22spec_detail_info%22%3Bs%3A0%3A%22%22%3Bs%3A12%3A%22content_type%22%3Bs%3A4%3A%22text%22%3Bs%3A10%3A%22media_type%22%3Bs%3A10%3A%22unmediated%22%3Bs%3A12%3A%22carrier_type%22%3Bs%3A15%3A%22online+resource%22%3Bs%3A3%3A%22uid%22%3Bs%3A1%3A%221%22%3Bs%3A7%3A%22authors%22%3Ba%3A9%3A%7Bi%3A0%3Ba%3A3%3A%7Bs%3A11%3A%22author_name%22%3Bs%3A11%3A%22Yanhao+Wang%22%3Bs%3A14%3A%22authority_type%22%3Bs%3A1